VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'What if we could take an existing video and then swap the character out with a new character using a reference image? Well, that\'s exactly what this new AI called Mocha does. This is a free and open-source AI tool by this orange team.'

[00:12] [scene:talk]
VISUAL:
AUDIO: 'And this allows you to replace any character in an existing video just with a reference image of your new character. And as you can see here, it\'s able to match all the movements of your original'

